<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_278_r1l26"><expan>winſh<ex>eim</ex></expan> . </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_278_r1l27"><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / Als man <expan>yecʒunde<ex>n</ex></expan> vaſt ſagt von cʒükunft <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l28"><expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> deʒ künigs <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / . <expan>Davo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l29"><expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etwas <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . So wiſſen wir ſelber noch nicht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_278_r1l30"><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> daʒ man lantmanſweıſe etc vt Sweinfürt / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_278" id="138v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Winsh<ex>eim</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als man <expan>yeczunde<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        vast sagt von czükunft <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> dez künigs <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ew <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etwas
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, so wissen wir selber
                        noch nicht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> daz
                        man lantmansweise etc. ut Sweinfürt.</ab>
</div>
